column6: Kaycem is using an ipad to work on human anatomy in procreate. He is currently focused on the lower half of the drawing|| which is a human figure with hand on hip and one hand extended outwards.
He is working on the fingers of the outstretched hand
his dog looks up at him
he is working on the right thigh of the figure.
he adds in the kneecap and continues his lines to the ankles.
He draws in the shoes to be almost the same as the reference lines.
He has zoomed out and sees the whole figure.
He has hidden his guide layer.
He duplicates his line layer and separates it from the original figure.
There are a good amount of Fs in the chat.
The lines look significantly darker and clearer.
